# File 'lib/dropbox_api/metadata/file_extensions_list.rb', line 5

def initialize(data)
  if !data.is_a?(Array) || data.any? { |v| !v.is_a? String }
    raise ArgumentError, "Invalid extension list: #{data.inspect}."
  end

  super(data)
end
